built on http://www.jamesyu.org/2011/01/27/cloudedit-a-backbone-js-tutorial-by-example/

key points
- see model for DM specific changes (DataMapper::MassAssignmentSecurity)
- see controller for DM specific changes

Otherwise, a simple illustration of Backbone.js built on previous tutorials.

suggestions and improvements welcome.
